author: Google
description:
YouTube partnered with Google DeepMind to bring a custom version of their most powerful video generation model, Veo 3, to YouTube. Veo 3 Fast is designed to work seamlessly in YouTube Shorts for millions of creators and users, for free. It generates outputs with lower latency at 480p so you can easily create video clips – and for the first time, with sound – from any idea, all from your phone. 

Tap the create button, then the sparkle icon in the top right corner to find our latest gen AI creation tools including Veo 3.

Currently rolling out in the United States, United Kingdom, Canada, Australia, and New Zealand, with plans to expand to more of you soon.

#Veo3 #GoogleDeepMind #YouTubeCreators
title: A new way to make Shorts just dropped ✨ Veo 3 is coming free to everyone in YouTube Shorts.
